    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币在 11 月的选举中如愿以偿。接下来该怎么办？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/crypto-got-what-it-wanted-in-the-us-election-here-s-what-s-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该行业现在正处于削弱金融规则的境地，这可能会保护消费者免受下一次加密货币崩盘的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/crypto-got-what-it-wanted-in-the-us-election-here-s-what-s-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 在加入纳斯达克 100 指数前购买更多比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-ahead-of-joining-nasdaq-100</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 是一家互联网时代的软件制造商，现已转型成为杠杆式比特币代理，通过出售股票又购买了价值 15 亿美元的加密货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-ahead-of-joining-nasdaq-100</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 13:07:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币创下 2021 年以来最长周涨幅纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对数字资产的支持，以及对即将将持有该代币的 MicroStrategy Inc. 纳入美国关键股票指数的乐观态度，比特币价格升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
